OL,3,CGoodbye ovens - Air fryers now UK's
OL,4,Cthird most-used appliance
OL,6,FAir fryers have become "a part of
OL,7,Feveryday life" in British kitchens,
OL,8,Franking as the third most-used
OL,9,Fappliance after toasters and microwave
OL,10,Fovens, according to a survey.
OL,12,FThe Good Food Nation study found that
OL,13,Fair fryer sales have surged, as their
OL,14,Fenergy efficiency appealed to
OL,15,Fhouseholds facing the cost-of-living
OL,16,Fcrisis.
OL,18,FThe survey, which interviewed 2,003 UK
OL,19,Fadults, found that 58% now use an air
OL,20,Ffryer, up from 46% last year.
