OL,3,CGoodbye ovens - Air fryers now UK's
OL,4,Cthird most-used appliance
OL,6,FTheir dominance was further cemented
OL,7,Fas 33% no longer use conventional
OL,8,Fovens.
OL,10,FDespite air fryers often claiming to
OL,11,Fmake perfect toast, 77% of those
OL,12,Fsurveyed still use a toaster, slightly
OL,13,Fmore than the 75% who use a microwave.
OL,15,FLily Barclay, content director for
OL,16,FGood Food, said: "The Good Food Nation
OL,17,Ffindings confirm our long-held
OL,18,Finstincts that air fryers, almost
OL,19,Funheard of two years ago, are now part
OL,20,Fof everyday life for the majority of
OL,21,Fhouseholds in the UK."
