OL,3,CGoodbye ovens - Air fryers now UK's
OL,4,Cthird most-used appliance
OL,6,FThe study also highlighted the diets
OL,7,Fand sustainable eating habits of Brits.
OL,9,FIt revealed that consumers continue to
OL,10,Feat meat an average of four days a
OL,11,Fweek, with just under a fifth (19%)
OL,12,Feating meat every day.
OL,14,FGood Food also made a "surprising"
OL,15,Ffinding; Millennials (aged 27 to 42)
OL,16,Fwere the most likely to eat meat
OL,17,Fdaily, with 26% doing so, followed by
OL,18,FGen Z (aged 16 to 26) at 24%.
